entries.journal_entry_description: Tanoa Vills can build you a sequencer, but she's missing some components. Get those for her.
entries.journal_entry_title: Get the Parts for a Sequencer
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Tanoa Vills needs an XJ5 circuit board. Mummer scientists have those, because they stole a shipment of them. Defeat Mummer scientists until you find an XJ5 circuit board.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Defeat Mummer Scientists to Find an XJ5 Circuit Board
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find 3 fractal transmitters. You can get them from old terminals that were dumped into a junk pile near Dee'ja Peak.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You need 8 octave regulators. Defeat Skaak Tipper machinists until you have them.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Defeat Skaak Tipper Machinists and Collect Octave Regulators
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Tanoa with the parts for the sequencer.
